author: cnbc.com
title: CORRECTING and REPLACING First National Bank Alaska Declares Dividend for Second Quarter 2018
text:
ANCHORAGE, Alaska--(BUSINESS WIRE)-- The beginning of the release should read: At the Board of Directors Meeting held April 25, 2018... (instead of At the Board of Directors Meeting held April 24, 2018...)
The corrected release reads:
FIRST NATIONAL BANK ALASKA DECLARES DIVIDEND FOR SECOND QUARTER 2018
At the Board of Directors Meeting held April 25, 2018, First National Bank Alaska (OTCBB:FBAK) declared a cash dividend of $25.00 per share, payable on June 15, 2018, to shareholders of record as of June 1, 2018.
